	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />256kbit RAM and EPROMs pinouts are almost the same, only the WR pin doesn't exists on ROMs, and the P pin doesn't exist on RAM (both should be put to VCC anyways).

		

		</td>
	</tr>
	</table>


